OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Fand scattered showers through the
OL,7,Fevening and overnight, these showers
OL,8,Fwill be heavy at times. It will be
OL,9,Frather windy around the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,12,Fscattered showers. Becoming mostly dry
OL,13,Fby the evening as showers fade out.
OL,14,FBreezy around the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA band
OL,17,Fof rain pushes east Friday with a few
OL,18,Fshowers following later. Bright spells
OL,19,Fand showers on Saturday. Dry and
OL,20,Fbright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
